nbtw狗引人裝修唔係因為想民意逆轉<br />\n而係想挫死有裝手足<br />\n民意係唔會因為裝修藍店而逆轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955ccf511bd8f072cf0d7846f48a8cd4d081fa73","tid":1801522,"uid":76395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:17:23.000Z","msg":"Btw連登準備兩極化討論和你shop<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位真係參與討論時記得用<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不推文回覆</span></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"4cd989a8a216a794640bdc83cc285d5edae1d450","tid":1801522,"uid":300264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:23:47.000Z","msg":"出嚟之前要清楚自己嘅目標 <br />\n<br />\n要快閃裝修嘅唔該唔好喺公海講 ，Blackblock 文具自己諗<br />\n<br />\n要和你shop嘅就一定街坊裝，博佢亂拉港豬藍絲 <br />\n<br />\n唔好畀人慫兩句又帶鎚仔文具， 一定要有獨立思考唔好人話乜就乜， 只要你做嘢之前諗下目標係乜分清楚，鬼冇咩可怕"},{"pid":"5d2f23e93c10bb6fd840c477154f432aede8b6e6","tid":1801522,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:23:58.000Z","msg":"德福和你shop應該係手足搞㗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801473</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"75f89b539ef5bb36602809e2999bf0f5cff35370","tid":1801522,"uid":2837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:28:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"997a168a23d8d7f38c51db06653f0117d718e905","tid":1801522,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6f4cc16891b0d91795c726ca481ce34a01efce","tid":1801522,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c003d08d4e5a5f59eeaea38f3c0779f3174b33e","tid":1801522,"uid":273716,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:14:13.000Z","msg":"口吻好奇怪 叫人帶鎚仔同文具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁直接叫人帶鎚仔去裝修<br />\n下隻字就叫人帶文具咁隱晦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係手足唔會咁講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw狗引人裝修唔係因為想民意逆轉<br />\n而係想挫死有裝手足<br />\n民意係唔會因為裝修藍店而逆轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:31:13.000Z","msg":"果句野係其中一隻狗講,但唔係搞手黎,跟住周圍係咁煲搞手係狗,搞到個搞手跳樓咁濟"},{"pid":"eb39fca441a8453403c294936d139656b31f550f","tid":1801522,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:31:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b978a6bdfd2fa6b26f56a7e722c3a7dc246448f6","tid":1801522,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:31:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83cc1c76a1ceba71824ede113d647da7a861e2f5","tid":1801522,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借個位黎用下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由窮爸爸富爸爸探討黃色經濟圈發展</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1801758/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1801758/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>黃色證券圈</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1798024/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1798024/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>黃色慈善圈</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1800956/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1800956/</a>"},{"pid":"1724f570eb87099d2278f1c9f9a86296da1824d3","tid":1801522,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:33:46.000Z","msg":"本身一日一post諗住今晚出post發悔氣屌架啦,點知呢個post又突然間上到熱門"},{"pid":"9c37a2a31eeb6445451bb020bb486aa77bcb1bb3","tid":1801522,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:34:04.000Z","msg":"和你shop必須要keep住做，諗方法改善，而唔係畀人唱淡幾句就放棄<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1797542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1797542</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2f8607e9a74bea26e84f1da3e3e94f2597f9b332","tid":1801522,"uid":152225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:34:05.000Z","msg":"根本唔使捉鬼，和理shop多人就成事。班狗佢9拉無用，根本無可能告得入，拉完又無證據最後實放人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬炒經濟，趕走支那"},{"pid":"b3802df58fec35a1cf9ec542e88872c50eec7a9c","tid":1801522,"uid":148355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:34:55.000Z","msg":"經過呢幾日和你shop，有幾點想補充：<br />\n<br />\n1.選址<br />\n和你shop唔論多人定少人join，都要揀人流多嘅場。港豬同遊客係最好嘅掩護。去人流少嘅場搞，啲狗任拉一個都係手足，咁佢地就更加肆無忌憚濫捕。<br />\n<br />\n2.衣著<br />\n我原本建議為咗減低被鎖定風險，和你shop時以彩虹戰衣代替black bloc。然而，如果著得太鮮色(例如紅)，同樣會畀狗鎖定，所以black bloc並非不可，而係要睇準時機換掉。如果著其他色，應以深色公廁款為佳。要謹記，唔單止現場有便衣，啲指揮狗都睇緊live。<br />\n<br />\n3.同便衣狗衝突<br />\n都係嗰句：首先咪撚狗，同佢地保持距離。吸取多次經驗，當佢地主動發難咬人時，請手足唔好為咗一時意氣打狗救人。一嚟啲狗係濫捕，被咬手足入罪機會極低；二嚟根本救唔到，其他便衣同防暴9秒9就嚟增援，打狗嘅結果就係襲警被斷正。如果便衣只係stop &amp; search，更加唔洗衝動，no gear出到嚟咪任佢查。"},{"pid":"cb48f19173340d48b4b97082da2d3d4d573c4244","tid":1801522,"uid":152225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:37:08.000Z","msg":"推！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d325457ef77a5ab9977228734f2cf8b37552a7d","tid":1801522,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:37:28.000Z","msg":"隔離講緊個活動係鬼搞個post起碼有1000隻5毛,屌你老味,入去辛苦到"},{"pid":"85c0ea1e6f42f0c2da40c91a869aca98914d3733","tid":1801522,"uid":51937,"like"